INCIPIT grimoire "civitas_template_context"

SIGILLUM LoopContext
  index: REX
  count: REX
  length: REX
  is_first: VERUM
  is_last: VERUM
FIN SIGILLUM

RITUALE tpl_loop_context(REX index, REX length) REDDE LoopContext
  EVOCA LoopContext ctx
  VINCIRE ctx.index AD index
  VINCIRE ctx.count AD index + 1
  VINCIRE ctx.length AD length
  VINCIRE ctx.is_first AD index == 0
  VINCIRE ctx.is_last AD index == length - 1
  REDDE ctx
EXPLICIT RITUALE

EXPLICIT grimoire
